    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここは……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Where is this...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278408</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この子たち……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>These children... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278488</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ファわわわわわわ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Waah! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>静かに。大きな声を出すと、
この子たちが目を覚まして
しまいますよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Quiet, please. If you shout any 
more you will wake the children.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ……あなたは……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who are you...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278768</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私はノルンと言います</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Please call me Norn. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノルン……
この子たちの……ママ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Norn, you say? Are you the children's mother? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いいえ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm afraid that's not the case. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279028</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もしかして……
ぼくを助けてくれたのは
あなたですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wait... Is it that...you were the one who saved me? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279216</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ええ。倒れていた貴方を
私がここまで連れてきました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Precisely. I found you collapsed on
the ground and brought you here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279216</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>貴方にこの子たち、
&lt;Dio&gt;と&lt;Mel&gt;ふたりの
親代わりをお願いするために</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>These infants are &lt;Dio&gt; and &lt;Mel&gt;. I want 
you to be these children's foster mother. </EnglishText>
      <Notes>Maybe adoptive mother?</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279284</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>親代わり……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Their foster mother...</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Maybe adoptive mother?</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ってぼくが！？
むりむりむりむり！
むりだかラ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Me? N-No way! That's completely impossible! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こんな小さいし、力もないし、
魔物が襲ってきたら、
ひとたまりもないです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't protect them from monsters.
I am small, powerless, and I'm not
even human like these kids... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279592</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この家は強力な結界に
守られています。
魔物は決して襲ってきません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You needn't worry, as this house is
surrounded by a magical barrier that
will protect you. Monsters have no
way through it. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、それでも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...still... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この子たちは、
運命の輪から
切り離された子</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>These children have limitless potential in their future, a 
recurring fate that they must meet. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いずれ世界を救うかもしれません。
あるいは滅ぼすかもしれません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They might try to make the world theirs. 
They might even try to destroy it. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ただ見守るだけでよいのです。
お願いします。彼らの魂の行く先を
……見守ってあげてください</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Despite that, I request that you look after and
protect them. It was a promise to him, to his 
soul. So please I must ask you to watch over 
these children.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review. Specifically "It was a promise to him, to his soul..."</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……？　あ、あれ！？
もしもシっ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eh? What!? H-Hello, are you there?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280132</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>このまま……逃げちゃう……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It looks like...she ran away? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>アブゥ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Waaaah! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>キャッキャッ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gahh! Gahh! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今日は厄日かな……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Today's not my lucky day, uh? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふふふっ……
こんにちは。はじめまして。
可愛い双子ちゃん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hehehe... Hi there. Nice to meet you, fair pair of twins... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_000_020_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぼくの名前は……エトスだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My name is...Ethos. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
